      "text": "美空から見ると、夜空の弓道は綺麗なんだな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。\n夜空は、弓を持つとすごく集中するんです。\n普段よりもっと静かで、でも強い感じがして。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "ごめん。\nでも、店長にも知ってほしいなって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
